Air magic harnesses the power of the ski: Air magic harnesses the power of the skies, commanding the wind, thunder, and lightning. Practitioners of this magic can summon storms, manipulate currents to buffet enemies, or strike with bolts of electricity. Air magic is known for its swiftness and unpredictability, embodying freedom and raw energy.
Anchored Casting turns the battlefield i: Anchored Casting turns the battlefield into a dynamic trap, allowing the caster to lay magical ambushes with precision and foresight.
Blazing Heat taps into the intense, radi: Blazing Heat taps into the intense, radiant power of the sun, allowing the caster to infuse their Fire Magic with a searing Solar (Light) energy.
Blistering Radiance channels the intense: Blistering Radiance channels the intense, searing power of Light Magic, making every spell cast a blinding and punishing force.
Caustic Cling enhances the corrosive pow: Caustic Cling enhances the corrosive power of Earth Magic, ensuring that its acid-based spells bite deep and linger long after their initial impact.
Clinging Shadow infuses Dark Magic with: Clinging Shadow infuses Dark Magic with an unsettling, oppressive force that lingers long after the spell is cast.
Commanding Spell enhances the caster’s a: Commanding Spell enhances the caster’s ability to manipulate and control others through Compulsion Magic.
Concussive Shock channels the raw force: Concussive Shock channels the raw force of storms into devastating precision, making “thunder” and “lightning” Air Magic spells deadlier than ever.
Dark magic draws power from the shadows,: Dark magic draws power from the shadows, weaving illusions, hiding truths, and striking from unseen places. It manipulates fear, stealth, and obscurity, making it as subtle as it is dangerous. While often maligned, Dark magic represents the necessity of secrecy and the power of the unknown.
Death magic taps into the finality of li: Death magic taps into the finality of life, drawing upon necrotic and infernal energies to decay, drain, or destroy. Practitioners can summon undead, sap life force, or unravel the essence of their enemies. This magic is feared for its associations with mortality and the unknown, though it holds a grim utility.
Dense Earth channels the steadfast and p: Dense Earth channels the steadfast and protective nature of the earth itself, bolstering defensive spells and enhancing the caster’s efficiency.
Driving Wave empowers the caster to chan: Driving Wave empowers the caster to channel the relentless force of water, enhancing both the precision and the impact of their spells.
